channel.title: Funny story / rs advice
channel.description:
i was trying to sell my pure ess but someguy on the forurms typed selling 2k nats 280k which was a good deal ( 140 ea) and then he realized his mistake and said he was sorry and that he was high. i decided to take advantage of him and first traded 3k pure ess for 1k nats and then i traded 2k pure ess for 1k nats, a very good very deal.
for the people who think my story is gay, remember the moral of it, dont play runescape when your wasted.
